movie.title: The Pirates
movie.description_intro: A band of pirates and a group of bandits fight to catch a gray whale that has swallowed a royal stamp.

movies.title: First Man
movies.summary: A Biopic on the life of the legendary American Astronaut Neil Armstrong from 1961-1969, on his journey to becoming the first human to walk the moon. Exploring the sacrifices and costs on the Nation and Neil himself, during one of the most dangerous missions in the history of space travel.

movies.title: Abbott and Costello Meet Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde
movies.title_english: Abbott and Costello Meet Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde
movies.title_long: Abbott and Costello Meet Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde (1953)
movies.summary: Slim and Tubby are American cops in London to study police tactics. They wind up in jail and are bailed out by Dr. Jekyll. Jekyll has been murdering fellow doctors who laugh at his experiments. He has more murders in mind. At one point the serum that turns Jekyll into the murderous Hyde gets injected into Tubby.

movies.title: Unbelievable!!!!!
movies.summary: Four astronauts travel to the Moon on a rescue mission to determine the fate of two NASA comrades who have not been heard from in several days. The individuals they find at the Lunar Base are not whom they appear to be and, through acts of trickery and deception, nearly succeed in killing our heroes. The four return to find that everyone on the planet has been transformed into a variant life-form. Aliens from Mars have conquered Earth and now seek to destroy the last remnants of humanity. The astronauts fight back and soon discover how to rid themselves of the alien threat.

movies.title: Transference: A Love Story
movies.summary: Katarina, a Norwegian nurse in London, embarks on a passionate affair with a fellow immigrant nurse that suffers the consequences of unresolved mental health issues from the lovers' secret pasts.
